@startuml
title E6-01 — Propose and Approve Debt Transaction\nActor and Decision View

left to right direction

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "Issuance\nOfficer" as Officer

rectangle "Debt Issuance Platform" as Platform {
  rectangle "Create and\nValidate Proposal" as Create
  rectangle "Control Approval\nWorkflow" as Control
  rectangle "Record Final\nDecision" as Record
}

actor "Treasury\nApprover" as Approver

Officer --> Create : Enters proposed\ntransaction terms

Create --> Officer : Returns validation\nresults

Officer --> Control : Submits valid\nproposal

Control --> Approver : Presents terms,\nexceptions and changes

Approver --> Control : Approves or\nreturns with reason

Control --> Record : Stores decision\nand status

Record --> Officer : Approved or\nchanges required

legend bottom
|= Actor |= Main question |
| Issuance Officer | What debt transaction are we proposing? |
| Platform | Is it complete, valid and properly controlled? |
| Treasury Approver | Should this transaction proceed? |

Main flow:
Propose → Validate → Submit → Decide → Record
endlegend

@enduml